{"title":"矿工同志　抚顺劳动模范大会上所见","authors":["臧云远"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":9,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿工同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抚顺劳动模范大会上所见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"臧云远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个挖煤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的工人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高高的嗓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挺着胸膛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"操着山东的口音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在劳模大会的台子上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿山的负责同志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑眯眯地望着他；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他缠着红彩绸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着大红花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"台下好几百劳模"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个劲鼓掌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢迎他讲话。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是他领着十八个矿工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下了竖井，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里的洞口不通风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那都是日本鬼子没好心眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只管挖煤不顾工人的命。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挖着挖着冒了顶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水淹了，火着了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就闭灭了坑闭灭了井。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反正乐得磨洋工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁管他生产减少"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活儿干不成！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刮民党来了要开工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人不起劲，没开成。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坑里充满瓦斯气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四五十度热得难走动；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛到了火山口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一不小心就完命。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是他们在坑口开个会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合计怎样才能行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今工人当了家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不再挨打受骂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干部和咱们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一块商量矿里大事情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十九个工友定计划，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先修好排气管排风道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"准备好铁铲铁锤和木料，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再下闭灭井，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爬到闭灭坑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着灭火的曹达，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扒个小小的窟窿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爬进去，抽出煤气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送进洞外的风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说干就干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一气八小时不停；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晕倒了，抬出来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏醒了，又下井，……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工友们全不顾性命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修好了闭灭的三号坑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个把月活儿十五天完成。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说起工人的勇敢和热情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"台下的掌声哄动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身后面高高的大画像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席和朱总司令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛听见了也高兴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墙壁上贴满了劳模的照片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的是作了二十年工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这回造出代用的机械；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的是厂里厂外鼓动着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大伙交拿了器材；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的是带头劳动好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的是发明了机件把生产提"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时窗外几十里矿坑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好几万工人正在劳动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工厂接着工厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烟囱挨着烟囱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一齐向着劳模大会"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听着热烈的鼓掌声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九月十五日"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}